name: Beans FPS
description: Beans FPS is a fast-paced, multiplayer first-person shooter game that you can play with your friends. This game offers 4 weapons (with a lot more to come)  to keep players engaged and entertained. With smooth gameplay and intense action, Beans FPS is sure to be a hit with players looking for a thrilling multiplayer experience. Join your friends and dominate the battlefield in Beans FPS!
